---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Our Services | IronLink Technologies">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1f3e60] to-[#365e8d] text-white text-center py-24 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">Precision IT Solutions That Move You Forward</h1>
    <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-white/90">From startups to enterprises, we deliver scalable technology strategies, hands-on support, and cybersecurity you can trust.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#f1f5f9] py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 text-left">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1f3e60] mb-3">🛡️ Cybersecurity & Compliance</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Protect your data and reputation with tailored security audits, managed detection & response, and compliance readiness for SOC2, HIPAA, and NIST.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-bold text-[#365e8d] hover:underline">Get Protected →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1f3e60] mb-3">☁️ Cloud Engineering</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Deploy faster and scale smarter. We design, migrate, and optimize cloud environments with AWS, Azure, and hybrid solutions.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-bold text-[#365e8d] hover:underline">Talk Cloud Strategy →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1f3e60] mb-3">🧠 Fractional CTO</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Don’t just hire tech support — gain an advisor. Our CTO services help shape product direction, vendor strategy, and future-proof roadmaps.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-bold text-[#365e8d] hover:underline">Request a Consultation →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1f3e60] mb-4">What Makes IronLink Different?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">We're more than a vendor — we’re your long-term strategic ally. Our engineers bring deep expertise and proactive mindset to every project.</p>
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-block bg-[#1f3e60] text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#274d72] transition">See Our Results</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#365e8d] to-[#1f3e60] text-white text-center py-20 px-6">
